{"entry_type":"warning","summary":"User preferences model (user-preferences.ts) assumes email-only — must be updated for multi-channel (SMS, webhook)","detail":"The UserPreferences model in src/models/user-preferences.ts was designed with email as the only notification channel (decision 01KN136P41W6A6AX61J2ZZJPZJ, assumption: "Email is currently the only notification channel"). With SMS now added, these issues need addressing:

